---
// AboutSection — WHITE background, clean, breathing
---
<section class="about section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ab-grid">

      <div class="ab-left reveal">
        <span class="section-tag">Who We Are</span>
        <h2>Nigeria's Most <span class="text-gradient">Experienced</span> Solar Company</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2008 and operating across Nigeria, TECIL Solar is the renewable energy division of Tecil Integrated Services Limited. For over 16 years we have delivered <strong>end-to-end solar solutions</strong> — from a single home installation to 60KW off-grid industrial systems.</p>
        <p>We don't chase the cheapest deal. We earn the right to be trusted — through technical depth, honest advice, and systems that outlast their warranties.</p>

        <div class="ab-values">
          <span class="av">Excellence</span>
          <span class="av">Innovation</span>
          <span class="av">Integrity</span>
          <span class="av">Sustainability</span>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-btns">
          <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">Our Track Record</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn-outline">Our Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ab-right">
        <div class="ab-stat-grid">
          <div class="ab-stat reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="ast-num">16+</div>
            <div class="ast-label">Years Operating</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-stat reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="ast-num">34+</div>
            <div class="ast-label">Corporate Projects</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-stat reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="ast-num">7</div>
            <div class="ast-label">Active Branches</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ab-stat reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="ast-num">15+</div>
            <div class="ast-label">Brand Partnerships</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ab-mission reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="abm-line"></div>
          <p class="abm-text">"To build a reputation as the leading, most knowledgeable, most reliable and most customer-friendly renewable energy company in Africa."</p>
          <span class="abm-cite">TECIL Solar Mission Statement</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about { background: #FFFFFF; }

.ab-grid {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:5rem; align-items:center;
}

.ab-left h2 { color:#111827; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
.ab-left p { margin-bottom:1rem; }
.ab-left p strong { color:#111827; font-weight:600; }

.ab-values { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin:1.5rem 0 2rem; }
.av {
  background:#FFF5EE; border:1.5px solid rgba(232,96,26,.25);
  color:#E8601A; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  font-size:.72rem; font-weight:700; padding:5px 13px;
  border-radius:100px; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase;
}
.ab-btns { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }

.ab-stat-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:2px; margin-bottom:2px; }
.ab-stat {
  background:#F7F8FA; padding:2rem 1.75rem;
  border:1px solid #E5E7EB;
  transition:all .3s ease; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.ab-stat::before {
  content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,#CC1417,#E8601A);
  transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left; transition:transform .3s ease;
}
.ab-stat:hover { background:#fff; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08); transform:translateY(-2px); }
.ab-stat:hover::before { transform:scaleX(1); }

.ast-num {
  font-family:'Big Shoulders Display',sans-serif;
  font-size:2.8rem; font-weight:900; color:#CC1417; line-height:1; margin-bottom:4px;
}
.ast-label { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:.75rem; font-weight:600; color:#6B7280; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; }

.ab-mission {
  background:#FFF1F1; border:1px solid rgba(204,20,23,.15);
  border-left:4px solid #CC1417; padding:1.5rem 1.75rem;
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px;
}
.abm-line { width:24px; height:2px; background:#CC1417; }
.abm-text { font-size:.9rem; color:#4B5563; font-style:italic; line-height:1.75; }
.abm-cite { font-size:.68rem; font-weight:700; color:#CC1417; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.1em; }

@media(max-width:900px){
  .ab-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:3rem}
}
</style>
